---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="footer" role="contentinfo">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="brand">
        <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="Guardian.Nine - Beranda">
          <img src="/images/Logo.png" alt="Guardian.Nine Logo" class="logo-icon" style="height: 48px; width: auto; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain;" />
          <span class="logo-text">GUARDIAN.<span class="text-primary">NINE</span></span>
        </a>
        <p>Meningkatkan performa atletik melalui desain dan teknologi. Berbasis di Sidoarjo, melayani pengiriman seluruh Indonesia.</p>
      </div>


      <div class="location" aria-labelledby="footer-location-heading">
        <h4 id="footer-location-heading">Lokasi Kami</h4>
        <address class="address-text">
          <p><strong>Jersey Kaos Guardian Nine Apparel</strong></p>
          <p>Sidoarjo, Jawa Timur</p>
        </address>
        <div class="map-container">
          <iframe 
            src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Jersey%20kaos%20Guardian%20Nine%20Apparel%20Sidoarjo&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed" 
            title="Lokasi Guardian.Nine di Google Maps"
            width="100%" 
            height="150" 
            style="border:0; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 1rem;" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} Guardian.Nine. Hak cipta dilindungi.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background: #050505;
    padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .logo-icon {
    height: 48px !important;
    max-height: 48px !important;
    width: auto !important;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
    image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;
  }

  .brand p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 250px;
  }

  .location h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .address-text {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  .address-text strong {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .visually-hidden {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .btn-sm {
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
